div.div: Closed #13572 [Bug]: Netdata service/daemon dies after startup with segfault in libuuid.so.1.3.0
Commented on #13572 [Bug]: Netdata service/daemon dies after startup with segfault in libuuid.so.1.3.0

@phiberoptick what worked for @harpo (still checking though) is to manually delete this line from the db (or wait for a nightly with a fix). In /var/cache/netdata you can use sqlite3 for netdata-meta.db and do a delete from chart where chart_id is null; . Could you try this to see if it fixes your case as well?
@MrZammler, that did it! Everything appears to be operating normally again. Thanks!
